snippet.title: Pandaclip: The Black Thief - Action RPG Shooter Trailer
snippet.description:
Pandaclip : The Black Thief is available on Google Play! 🔽
http://bit.ly/2KioNhv

Pandaclip: The Black Thief is an epic Offline Action RPG Shooter with cute anime girls. Chiwa and friends want to go camping, but suddenly a problem occurs and they have to fight the invasion of black bears who steal their food.

Help Chiwa and friends in their quest to defeat the black bear from stealing food! 🐼
